WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: TLS rotation — every operator needs to do this eventually.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: a fresh certificate is dropped into the rotation directory.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:25.000
narrator: octravpn-node accepts SIGHUP and reloads TLS material live.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
narrator: in-flight tailscale connections are not torn down.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:45.000
narrator: a curl against the control plane confirms the new chain.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:55.000
narrator: the old certificate can be revoked once the rollout is clean.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:05.000
narrator: rotation is now a one-step operation, not an outage.
